\lang1033\b\f1\fs16 Black to play\lang1042\b0\f0\fs18
\lang1033\f1\fs16 White exchanges 1 for 2 and then White attaches at 3.  We'll be studying variations from this shape.  When Black plays at 4 White answers with 5, how should Black respond?  \lang1042\f0\fs18


