;B[ee]LB[gd:1][db:2][ff:3][ee:4]CR[cd]C[Dia.3 White 3 is overplay

If White doesn't like the result from the previous diagram he can draw back wiht 1 in reponse to the marked Black stone.  Black should just cut.

White's cut at 3 is overplay.  Black draws back with 4 and White is in for a very disadvantageous fight.  This is a success for Black.
\lang1042\f1\fs18

