;B[cd]LB[ec:1][db:2][cd:3][ed:A][ee:B]C[Dia.3 Easy to understand

Black could try and dansu at 1 then connect at 3.  This is the easy way to play.  There aren't many variations.  Next, White plays at A and Black could respond at B and get a very thick shape.
\lang1042\f1\fs18

